cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper deals with object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves a deep learning model, specifically a mixture of Gaussians, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques for qualitative analysis, which could potentially fall under computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on two datasets, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) as they involve images and annotations.
